\c 23
\s Kufa kwaSara
\p
\v 1 Zvino Sara wakagara makore ane zana namakumi maviri nama­nomwe; ndiwo makore oupenyu hwaSara.
\v 2 Sara akafa paKiriyatiabha (rimwe zita ndiHebhuroni) panyika yeKanani; Abhurahamu akauya kuzochema Sara nokumuririra.
\p
\v 3 Zvino Abhurahamu akasimuka pa­nowakafa wake, akataurirana navana vaHeti, akati,
\v 4 Ndiri mweni nomutorwa pakati penyu, ndipei nzvimbo yokuviga pakati penyu, ive nzvimbo yangu, kuti ndivige wakafa wangu, ndirege ku­muona.
\p
\v 5 Vana vaHeti vakapindura Abhura­hamu, vakati kwaari,
\v 6 Chitinzwai, ishe wedu, imwi muri muchinda waMwari pa­kati pedu; vigai wakafa wenyu pabwiro hwakanaka pakati pamabwiro edu ose; hakuna munhu pakati pedu angakunyimai bwiro hwake, kuti muvige wakafa we­nyu.
\v 7 Ipapo Abhurahamu wakasimuka akakotamira pasi pamberi pavanhu ve­nyika iyo, ivo vana vaHeti,
\v 8 akataurirana navo, akati, Kana muchitenda kuti ndi­vige wakafa wangu, ndirege kumuona, chindinzwai, mundikumbirire kuna Efu­roni, mwanakomana waZohari,
\v 9 kuti andipe bako reMakapera, raanaro, riri pamagumo emunda wake, andipe iroro, ndiripe mutengo wose, ive nzvimbo ya­ngu yokuviga pakati penyu.
\p
\v 10 Efuroni zvino wakanga agere pa­kati pavana vaHeti; Efuroni, muHeti, akapindura Abhurahamu, vana vaHeti, vachizvinzwa, ivo vose vaipinda pasuo reguta rake, akati,
\v 11 Kwete, ishe wangu, chindinzwai; teererai, ndinokupai munda, nairo bako ririmo, ndinokupai iro; ndino­kupai izvozvo pamberi pavana vavanhu vangu; vigai henyu wakafa wenyu.
\v 12 Abhurahamu akakotama pamberi pava­nhu venyika iyo,
\v 13 akataura naEfuroni, vanhu venyika iyo vachizvinzwa, achiti, Kana uchida, chinditeerera hako, ndi­chakupa mutengo womunda, uugamu­chire kwandiri, kuti ndivige wakafa wa­ngupo.
\v 14 Efuroni akapindura Abhurahamu, akati kwaari,
\p
\v 15 Ishe wangu, chinditeererai; mu­nda unotengwa namashekeri esirivha ana mazana mana, chingava chinyiko pakati pangu newe? Vigai henyu wakafa we­nyu.
\v 16 Abhurahamu akateerera Efuroni. Abhurahamu akayerera Efuroni mashe­keri esirivha aakareva, vana vaHeti va­chizvinzwa, mashekeri esirivha ana ma­zana mana, avanotenga nawo kuvatengesi.
\p
\v 17 Naizvo munda waEfuroni, wa­kanga uri paMakapera pakatarisana neMamure, munda nebako rakanga ririmo, nemiti yose yakanga iri mumunda neya­kanga iri panyika yose yakapoteredza,
\v 18 zvikava zvaAbhurahamu pamberi pa­vana vaHeti, pamberi pavose vaipinda pasuo reguta rake.
\p
\v 19 Shure kwaizvozvo Abhurahamu akaviga Sara, mukadzi wake, mubako romunda weMakapera, pakatarisana neMamure (rimwe zita ndiHebhuroni), pa­nyika yeKanani.
\v 20 Zvino munda nebako rakanga ririmo zvakasimbisiwa kuna Abhurahamu navana vaHeti, kuti zvive zvake, ikava nzvimbo yake yokuviga.
